Helen of Troy Corp said it filed withthe Securities and Exchange Commission a registration statementcovering a 20 mln dlr issue of covertible subordinateddebentures due 2007.    Proceeds will be used for general corporate purposes,including possible repayment of bank debt, product developmentand possible acquisitions, Helen of Troy said.    The company named Drexel Burnham Lambert Inc as soleunderwriter of the offering. Reuter&#3;